data.description: We are pleased to present a beautiful house with a POOL that offers both comfort and convenience. Situated in a fantastic location, you'll have easy access to supermarkets, banks, restaurants, gas stations, and much more. One of the standout features of this house is the inviting pool, which promises endless hours of relaxation and enjoyment. Imagine unwinding after a long day by taking a refreshing dip or simply lounging on the poolside. To top it off, there's also a screened porch, providing a serene space to savor the outdoors. We understand the convenience of having laundry facilities readily available, which is why this property offers a washer and dryer inside the property. This is a remarkable opportunity that you won't want to miss. Come and explore the potential this house holds for creating a dream home. Contact us today to schedule a showing of this delightful property. BRAND NEW ROOF!!!
